      "name": "Grid convergence index study for pump rotor region",
      "description": "Three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.7M elements) were evaluated. Grid Convergence Index for the volume-averaged shear stress scalar was 1.8% on the fine mesh, demonstrating discretization error is well controlled. The medium mesh (5.8M) was selected for production runs based on accuracy-cost trade-off."
    }
