      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used under a validated installation qualified per ISO 9001 procedures. The solver release notes confirm all applicable verification test cases pass. Version control of case files was maintained in a Git repository with audit trail. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
