      "rationale": "The ANSYS Fluent MRF rotating frame benchmark for a centrifugal impeller reproduced the Taylor-Couette analytic velocity profile to within 0.6%. Internal pipe flow pressure drop matched the Hagen-Poiseuille solution to within 0.3%. Code verification is confirmed adequate for MRL 2."
