      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments replicate the device geometry, operating regime, and fluid properties of the COU to a degree appropriate for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the same FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry used in the COU simulations. Operating conditions span the full 5 flow-speed combinations specified in the COU. The blood analog fluid matches clinical blood viscosity at operating temperature. Validation activities are judged highly relevant to the COU; no significant scenario gaps were identified that would reduce confidence in the model predictions."
    },
