      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; commercial solver quality assurance is accepted as sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit assessment of numerical solver error beyond software QA is not required. The commercial solver's internal error controls (residual convergence to 1e-5, imbalance monitoring) were confirmed active. This factor is accepted as not-assessed per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
