      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal use-error assessment is not required. The simulation was conducted by a PhD-level biofluid mechanics engineer with 8 years of CFD experience. All case setup files were independently reviewed by a second qualified analyst. Use error risk is accepted as a residual at this model risk level."
    },
    {
