      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; published literature support for RANS turbulence modeling in blood pump applications is accepted.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model is widely applied in blood pump CFD per published literature (Hariharan et al., Fraser et al.). At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required. The use of RANS is an accepted modeling assumption; model form uncertainty is acknowledged as a residual risk consistent with MRL 2 scoping."
